  "rationale": "<p>Setting the right-hand sides equal: <i>x</i> + 5 = <i>x</i>&sup2; + 12<i>x</i> + 35. Rearranging: <i>x</i>&sup2; + 11<i>x</i> + 30 = 0. Factoring: (<i>x</i> + 5)(<i>x</i> + 6) = 0, so <i>x</i> = &minus;5 or <i>x</i> = &minus;6. The greatest is &minus;5.</p>",
